    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"DAA Taxa\"\n---\n\n\n\n\n# Differential abundance analysis\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n\nAnalysis information:\n\n-   Method: maaslin3\n-   Taxonomic level: species, genus, family, phylum\n-   Group variable: diet\n-   Formula used: ~ diet * time + (1 | id)\n-   Correction: Benjamini-Hochberg FDR adjustment\n-   Detection threshold: 0.001\n-   Prevalence threshold: 0.1\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n\n\nFor a complete table of maaslin3 results, see [Species](https://github.com/openresearchlabs/OGB_project/blob/main/output/daa/daa_taxa/species/all_results.tsv), [genus](https://github.com/openresearchlabs/OGB_project/blob/main/output/daa/daa_taxa/genus/all_results.tsv), [phylum](https://github.com/openresearchlabs/OGB_project/blob/main/output/daa/daa_taxa/phylum/all_results.tsv), [family](https://github.com/openresearchlabs/OGB_project/blob/main/output/daa/daa_taxa/family/all_results.tsv)\n\nThe following tables lists all associations that pass MaAsLin 3's significance threshold for joint or individual q-values, ordered by increasing individual q-value.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"datatables html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-e168cd353be4d034a053\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-e168cd353be4d034a053\">{\"x\":{\"filter\":\"none\",\"vertical\":false,\"caption\":\"<caption>Table of significant features for species - Total features analyzed: 215<\\/caption>\",\"data\":[[\"Clostridiales_bacterium_KLE1615\",\"Clostridiales_bacterium_KLE1615\",\"GGB34797_SGB14322\",\"Lawsonibacter_asaccharolyticus\",\"Blautia_wexlerae\"],[\"diet\",\"diet\",\"diet\",\"time\",\"diet\"],[\"rice:time\",\"rice\",\"rice\",\"time\",\"rice\"],[1.75611114922684,-3.02380668154576,-3.1539747673809,-0.519554697583376,0.0252582685280507],[0.0841241150871211,0.0859969474579306,0.0859969474579306,0.591306982726054,1],[0.0851304677486186,0.0870205308659241,0.0870205308659241,0.0106719743481932,0.0001314321793028],[\"abundance\",\"abundance\",\"abundance\",\"abundance\",\"abundance\"]],\"container\":\"<table class=\\\"display\\\">\\n  <thead>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th>feature<\\/th>\\n      <th>metadata<\\/th>\\n      <th>value<\\/th>\\n      <th>coef<\\/th>\\n      <th>qval_individual<\\/th>\\n      <th>qval_joint<\\/th>\\n      <th>model<\\/th>\\n    <\\/tr>\\n  <\\/thead>\\n<\\/table>\",\"options\":{\"pageLength\":6,\"dom\":\"Bfrtip\",\"columnDefs\":[{\"targets\":5,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatSignif(data, 3, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":4,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatSignif(data, 3, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":3,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatSignif(data, 3, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"className\":\"dt-right\",\"targets\":[3,4,5]},{\"name\":\"feature\",\"targets\":0},{\"name\":\"metadata\",\"targets\":1},{\"name\":\"value\",\"targets\":2},{\"name\":\"coef\",\"targets\":3},{\"name\":\"qval_individual\",\"targets\":4},{\"name\":\"qval_joint\",\"targets\":5},{\"name\":\"model\",\"targets\":6}],\"order\":[],\"autoWidth\":false,\"orderClasses\":false,\"lengthMenu\":[6,10,25,50,100]}},\"evals\":[\"options.columnDefs.0.render\",\"options.columnDefs.1.render\",\"options.columnDefs.2.render\"],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"datatables html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-1adb2f8066d6ac83d16a\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-1adb2f8066d6ac83d16a\">{\"x\":{\"filter\":\"none\",\"vertical\":false,\"caption\":\"<caption>Table of significant features for species - Total features analyzed: 215<\\/caption>\",\"data\":[[\"Blautia_wexlerae\",\"Lawsonibacter